  "prompt": "Where can I get IIIT hyderabad question paper of 2016 for MTech of CS branch?",
  "response": "Obtaining past question papers for specific academic institutions such as IIIT Hyderabad can be done through several channels:\n\n1. **Official University Website:** Check if IIIT Hyderabad has an online repository or archives section where past papers may be available for download.\n\n2. **Library:** University libraries often keep past examination papers for student reference. Visit the IIIT Hyderabad library and inquire if they have the 2016 MTech CS branch papers.\n\n3. **Faculty Members:** Contact professors or the academic department at IIIT Hyderabad. They might be able to provide past papers or direct you to where you can find them.\n\n4. **Peer Networks:** Reach out to current students or alumni from IIIT Hyderabad. They might have saved their old question papers and can share them with you.\n\n5. **Online Educational Forums and Websites:** Platforms like Quora, Reddit, and educational forums might have users who have uploaded past papers. Additionally, dedicated educational websites sometimes collect and provide past papers from various institutions.\n\n6. **Social Media Groups:** Facebook groups, LinkedIn groups, or WhatsApp groups for IIIT Hyderabad students and alumni might be useful for networking and requesting past papers.\n\n7. **Student Affairs Office:** The student affairs or academic affairs office at IIIT Hyderabad can sometimes provide assistance or guidance on where to find past papers.\n\nAlways ensure you have proper authorization and comply with any policies or guidelines set by IIIT Hyderabad when accessing these resources.",
